      "name": "Hemolysis bench-to-CFD comparison — Q1 2026 release candidate",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted hemolysis index against in-vitro measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump test rig across five operating points. Validation was executed under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which is considered by the analysis team to be effectively the same build as the released version 2026-q1-build-7. No re-execution of the validation suite was performed under the released solver binary; the team judged the single patch-level revision (promotion of the rc2 tag to the release tag) to introduce no numerically material changes to the hemolysis transport solver. This judgment was not independently verified and no regression test log under the released build was archived.",
